title: How Did the Celtics Turn Their Season Around? | Weekends With Wos
description:
Wos is joined by The Athletic’s Jared Weiss to talk about the Boston Celtics. They discuss the Celtics' early-season struggles and what looked different about them during their nine-game winning streak (1:49), the chemistry between Jaylen Brown and Jayson Tatum (11:45), what this team’s potential is in the playoffs, and much more (22:53).

Host: Wosny Lambre
Guest: Jared Weiss
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
